feel any better...

38:58.161 --> 39:00.816
It's been a while
since I've wanted

39:00.860 --> 39:03.558
to listen to jazz with someone.

39:03.602 --> 39:05.865
- Actually...

39:05.908 --> 39:07.519
that does.

39:09.172 --> 39:10.609
- The Blue Danube--
- Mm-hmm.

39:10.652 --> 39:13.655
- Has a standing house band
on Tuesday.

39:13.699 --> 39:15.788
Now, we could meet here

39:15.831 --> 39:18.617
