39:18.660 --> 39:20.619
- Yes, that sounds--

39:20.662 --> 39:22.316
that sounds great.

39:22.360 --> 39:25.754
- Great, okay.
- [laughs]

39:25.798 --> 39:28.540
All right, Tuesday.

39:28.583 --> 39:30.324
