39:32.457 --> 39:33.414
- [laughs]

39:33.458 --> 39:36.809
♪

39:36.852 --> 39:39.072
- Well, I'm glad you called.

39:39.115 --> 39:41.422
To be honest, I thought
this was going the other way.

39:41.466 --> 39:42.728
- How come?

39:42.771 --> 39:46.122
- Well, you definitely
took your time.

39:46.166 --> 39:49.082
- Well, I--I just needed
to be sure.

39:51.127 --> 39:52.868
