this whole thing is.

41:19.955 --> 41:21.957
- Well, that's not
a bad place to start.

41:22.001 --> 41:23.350
- Yes, yes.

41:23.393 --> 41:26.440
Mr. Miles, the atheist.

41:26.484 --> 41:30.444
