41:36.929 --> 41:38.757
What about the God account?

41:38.800 --> 41:40.889
This is the second time
in the past few months

41:40.933 --> 41:43.849
that God has sent me a sign.
- Oh, yeah?

41:43.892 --> 41:45.546
You have to tell us the story?

41:45.590 --> 41:50.986
- Well, I was driving
a gentleman six weeks ago.

41:51.030 --> 41:52.814
The traffic was very bad,

41:52.858 --> 41:54.337
so I decided
to take a shortcut.

41:54.381 --> 41:57.340
I turned right and boom,
there's an accident.

41:57.384 --> 41:58.864
A lady was hit by a car,

41:58.907 --> 42:00.779
and she was laying
in the middle of the street.

42:00.822 --> 42:03.172
My passenger
jumps out of the car

42:03.216 --> 42:04.565
and runs to help the lady.

42:04.609 --> 42:06.654
It turns out he was a doctor.

42:06.698 --> 42:08.264
♪

42:08.308 --> 42:11.441
